      • buildFractionMaxDenominator

        public static SimpleFraction buildFractionMaxDenominator(double value,
                                                         int maxDenominator)
        Create a fraction given the double value and either the maximum error allowed or the maximum number of denominator digits.(给定双倍值以及允许的最大误差或最大分母数字数，创建一个分数。)
        Parameters:
        value - the double value to convert to a fraction.(值-要转换为分数的双倍值。)
        maxDenominator - maximum denominator value allowed.(max分母-允许的最大分母值。)
        Throws:
        java.lang.RuntimeException - if the continued fraction failed to converge.(java.lang. Runtime异常-如果连续分数未能收敛。)
        java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - if value > Integer.MAX_VALUE(Java.lang. IllegalArgumentExcept-如果值> RST.MAX_UTE)
